sources.description: THE FACE ON THE BARROOM FLOOR (1914)   Based on the poem of the same title by Hugh Antoine d'Arcy Starring: Charlie Chaplin, Vivian Edwards, Cecile Arnold, Jess Dandy,  Edward Nolan, Charles Bennett, Chester Conklin, Hank Mann, Harry McCoy, Fritz Schade Directed by Chaplin Keystone Film Company William Thomas Sherman, wts@gunjones.com, http://www.mn-hp.com
